c', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/79921/', '', 'Paritaprevir, Glecaprevir, Simeprevir, Amprenavir, Cabotegravir, Valaciclovir, Zanamivir, Lenacapavir, Telaprevir, Velpatasvir, Etravirine, More', 'Interferon alfa-n1, Oprelvekin, Sipuleucel-T, Elapegademase, Peginterferon alfa-2a, Ropeginterferon alfa-2b, Interferon alfacon-1, Sargramostim, Histamine, Aldesleukin, Pegademase, More', 1767369485);
